@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}


<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }


        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .policy {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

       



    </style>
</head>

<content id="content" class="flex-column">
    
    <h1> The Ashley's Store Policies Page </h1>
    <br />

    <section class="policy">
        <br />
   
        <h4>Return Policy</h4>
        <p>At Ashley's Store, we want you to be satisfied with your purchase. We accept returns within 30 days of the purchase date. Items must be in their original condition, unworn, unwashed, and with tags attached. Please keep your receipt or proof of purchase handy when initiating a return.</p>
        <p>If the return is due to our error or a defective product, we will cover the return shipping costs. However, for other returns, customers are responsible for return shipping fees. Refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days after we receive the returned item.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy">
        <h4>Shipping Policy</h4>
        <p>We offer free standard shipping for orders above $50 within the United States. For orders below $50, a flat rate of $5 will be applied. Expedited shipping options are available at an additional cost. Please allow 1-2 business days for processing before your order is shipped. Once shipped, you'll receive a tracking number via email to monitor your package.</p>
        <p>Note that shipping times may vary depending on the destination. International shipping is available with applicable shipping charges and delivery times based on the destination country's customs and regulations.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Additional sections for other policies -->

    <section class="policy">
        <h4>Privacy Policy</h4>
        <p>We prioritize the privacy and security of our customers' information. Any personal information collected during your shopping experience, including name, address, email, and payment details, is solely used for processing orders and enhancing your shopping experience with us. We do not share or sell your information to third parties.</p>
        <p>Our website may use cookies to improve functionality and provide a personalized experience. By using our site, you consent to the use of cookies in accordance with our Cookie Policy.</p>
    </section>


</content>

